data.meta_description: Dongyangopelta yangyanensis name in 2013 Zhejiangosaurus lishuiensis name in 2007 They were found in Zhejiang province. They're about the same size, same era, and closely related. I was commissioned to make a Zhejiangosaurus sculpture in 2017 for special exhibition. And commissioned to make a Dongyangopelta 3D model in 2022,  also revise Zhejiangosaurus 3D model at the same time. I let two model walk together in rendering here.
